{"tid":1338142,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"「唔該幫手推」西環行山路線","createTime":"2019-07-21T12:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-21T13:41:00.000Z","uid":164584,"like":11,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"65b24489b278628935a16c7aa967a1b326fa1e67","tid":1338142,"uid":164584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"今日發夢見到好多巴打絲打都帶哂裝備行山。<br />\n<br />\n其實大家知唔知道西營盤（中聯辦上方）有座龍虎<br />\n<br />\n山都好好行架，夜晚有啲位仲有街燈添。<br />\n<br />\n仲有仲有龍虎山可以去到中環，甚至華富，四通八達非常方便。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家不妨去行夜山。<br />\n<br />\n推比發緊夢既巴打絲打。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ce8d680d3bef99efc3c9c31e2b6853acbb2058a1","tid":1338142,"uid":164584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"65b24489b278628935a16c7aa967a1b326fa1e67","tid":1338142,"uid":164584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:19:58.000Z","msg":"今日發夢見到好多巴打絲打都帶哂裝備行山。<br />\n<br />\n其實大家知唔知道西營盤（中聯辦上方）有座龍虎<br />\n<br />\n山都好好行架，夜晚有啲位仲有街燈添。<br />\n<br />\n仲有仲有龍虎山可以去到中環，甚至華富，四通八達非常方便。<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大家不妨去行夜山。<br />\n<br />\n推比發緊夢既巴打絲打。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/lomore_bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:20:44.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"43fa52e77f72349fc7a41c6b46f09603321a43ba","tid":1338142,"uid":164584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:21:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"52a92d0d02306d99c9281ac4c806e6bf4896c63b","tid":1338142,"uid":164584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:21:19.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e7a96d5690ae2050d49647628ce2601cf3d5fee5","tid":1338142,"uid":83094,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:24:39.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d39718b3ffe34b9e9ff77fcd731ef50e6f4074cc","tid":1338142,"uid":164584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:27:49.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"d7c79c56dbfe0f966e999eed285fda60292f1872","tid":1338142,"uid":163001,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:28:16.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"952d7c36c7fb39c653786ce79a91b1d3b6c365bc","tid":1338142,"uid":255222,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:28:46.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"98db9724855b9490a52c4c2662cbf4f711b8bfc7","tid":1338142,"uid":216276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:29:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>GO TO HILL</strong></span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b690082748541aff98de6a41dcc5e4216b54d0d8","tid":1338142,"uid":263344,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:33:46.000Z","msg":"行山樂"},{"pid":"c6394ea51a2f4e85934fb1ecbd8621213043a866","tid":1338142,"uid":164584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:35:29.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"fdccddbee3f5848e3d3c3931946b472232facd98","tid":1338142,"uid":253983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:45:09.000Z","msg":"十張圖教你上龍虎山<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/spH0WHC.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FspH0WHC.jpg&h=fed12df0&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n喺西邊街上到英皇書院之後向東面(左手邊)行，一直行見到匯豐分行，就運匯豐分行嗰邊行上柏道，經聖士提反女子中學(會途經公務員宿舍)，一直行行行行到見到有條斜路上，不過唔好行條斜路咁笨，有兩條樓梯直上嘅<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/QYFYJou.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQYFYJou.jpg&h=53fa14f3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上到福苑就係一條長命斜(旭龢道)，中間會有個花園，一直行行到有個13號巴士站，你望對面馬路好似一面牆咁，中間有棵樹，然後對面有條斜路上(克頓道)。過對面馬路去克頓道<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O3jFWJH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO3jFWJH.jpg&h=eeb4ec0b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上到克頓道你會見到兩邊都係豪宅，繼續上。沿途有時會有車/的士上落，記得睇車。過左最後一間豪宅就差唔多開始條龍虎山晨運徑喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0QTn93U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0QTn93U.jpg&h=89376a92&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢度開始係龍虎山晨運徑，沿途會有路牌標示你行左幾多米(每百米一個)。喺二百米左右會有個公廁，四百米左右會有個維多利亞城界碑，六百米會有大大個牌寫住龍虎山郊野公園，然後一U-turn會見到有條分岔路(中間多條石級)，行左邊嗰條<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3cKbiXB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3cKbiXB.jpg&h=f7b95664&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n如果你喺個分岔路行石級就會上左去松林廢堡同燒烤場，其實都可以落得番晨運徑嘅。如果喺個分岔路行左邊就會繼續喺晨運徑，呢度開始會少啲遊樂設施(因為啲遊樂設施去哂松林廢堡同燒烤場度)<br />\n<br />\n未完待續"},{"pid":"6c0d051d3814d7473b95af5517c5d4741b34046d","tid":1338142,"uid":253983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c8d7BKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc8d7BKQ.jpg&h=8d79909f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼續上，呢度應該係九百米至一千三百/一千四百米左右。呢度啲樹高啲遮得密啲<br />\n留意番，其實去到呢度都仲係斜路，不過就快行完啲斜路嗱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yo1EsRD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyo1EsRD.jpg&h=fc9aa30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行到呢度你會見到第二間公廁(一千六百米)，之後上去你會見到一個公園仔(臨時休憩處)，嗰度朝早會有好多阿婆阿伯做運動打牙骹嘅。呢度開始就係平路，去到克頓道、夏力道同盧吉道交界，你可以向前行去夏力道繼續行晨運徑，短啲而且舒服啲，又可以U-turn去行盧吉道，條路就長啲(去凌霄閣嘅路程係夏力道double)而且有一半係暗斜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S9AU1bU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS9AU1bU.jpg&h=c4758a26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢一帶都係好舒服嘅平路，去到二千一百米又會見到啲運動設施<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWKiJqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWKiJqw.jpg&h=15f4705a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n運動設施(夏力道健身徑)大概長二百米，之後再行前嗰段路會比較窄，但行經瀑布(二千六百米)打後又會闊番<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2zCexk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2zCexk.jpg&h=7fa03af9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再行多二百米度就行完成條晨運徑喇，你到時已經可以見到凌霄閣同山頂廣場。如果覺得行到凌霄閣唔夠喉，可以轉上柯士甸山道上Victoria Peak，不過嗰度開始唔係晨運徑，所以盡量行人路小心車，而且將會係極斜，自己衡量下喇。嗰度應該亦都可以截的士<br />\n<br />\n注意，呢條山路體力須求極大，亦都比較費時時，大概要預一個鐘先行完，請量力而為"},{"pid":"c143402f26093cb2581725ba20debd889ad5f80e","tid":1338142,"uid":258010,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:53:01.000Z","msg":"如果行到出中環 畢打街近蘭桂坊個邊有車出南區華富，可以走佬避地鐵"},{"pid":"79f47bf5d352e8b66f9a1939361437c638800bec","tid":1338142,"uid":164584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6c0d051d3814d7473b95af5517c5d4741b34046d","tid":1338142,"uid":253983,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:51:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c8d7BKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc8d7BKQ.jpg&h=8d79909f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼續上，呢度應該係九百米至一千三百/一千四百米左右。呢度啲樹高啲遮得密啲<br />\n留意番，其實去到呢度都仲係斜路，不過就快行完啲斜路嗱<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/yo1EsRD.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fyo1EsRD.jpg&h=fc9aa30c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n行到呢度你會見到第二間公廁(一千六百米)，之後上去你會見到一個公園仔(臨時休憩處)，嗰度朝早會有好多阿婆阿伯做運動打牙骹嘅。呢度開始就係平路，去到克頓道、夏力道同盧吉道交界，你可以向前行去夏力道繼續行晨運徑，短啲而且舒服啲，又可以U-turn去行盧吉道，條路就長啲(去凌霄閣嘅路程係夏力道double)而且有一半係暗斜<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/S9AU1bU.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FS9AU1bU.jpg&h=c4758a26&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢一帶都係好舒服嘅平路，去到二千一百米又會見到啲運動設施<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sWKiJqw.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsWKiJqw.jpg&h=15f4705a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n運動設施(夏力道健身徑)大概長二百米，之後再行前嗰段路會比較窄，但行經瀑布(二千六百米)打後又會闊番<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/C2zCexk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FC2zCexk.jpg&h=7fa03af9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再行多二百米度就行完成條晨運徑喇，你到時已經可以見到凌霄閣同山頂廣場。如果覺得行到凌霄閣唔夠喉，可以轉上柯士甸山道上Victoria Peak，不過嗰度開始唔係晨運徑，所以盡量行人路小心車，而且將會係極斜，自己衡量下喇。嗰度應該亦都可以截的士<br />\n<br />\n注意，呢條山路體力須求極大，亦都比較費時時，大概要預一個鐘先行完，請量力而為"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T12:55:38.000Z","msg":"唔該巴打<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"465c1b5a47f07bdb97c3fe2e30ec098f06826356","tid":1338142,"uid":164584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:17:28.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"c5b64a1bdaa268a2248bc77264812d5e9c8d2df7","tid":1338142,"uid":30105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:20:29.000Z","msg":"Pish"},{"pid":"ecd795f47a47f44b3c8b788ce53ec9bc2dcc0d35","tid":1338142,"uid":30105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:20:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b81708d936a4af92f34ba513258801a3ab7564e4","tid":1338142,"uid":164584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:20:58.000Z","msg":"自推"},{"pid":"bca079bcda9cf90af158bb6c6678cc4baa924aea","tid":1338142,"uid":30105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:20:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1073e85cddf5412280d8e7171b15bb1424317609","tid":1338142,"uid":30105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:21:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76a958a230f40e9e848d38983213d2cfd60c3290","tid":1338142,"uid":164584,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:24:47.000Z","msg":"推推推"},{"pid":"1e6b7d48208b6fdbb36097ba04134bba27eb0562","tid":1338142,"uid":30105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:40:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7f970b8b84a449ca0e0fa854e9f6b1cb89276e5c","tid":1338142,"uid":30105,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-21T13:41:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}